Usage: BIND <key> GROW_WINDOW
  This function increases the size of the current window by one line
  if there is room.

See Also: 
  BIND HIDE_WINDOW
  BIND KILL_WINDOW
  BIND LIST_WINDOWS
  BIND NEW_WINDOW
  BIND SHRINK_WINDOW
